&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;💙 Join our team as a Night Shift Nurse where the vibes are calmer, the traffic is better, caffeine and late-night snacks are never judged. ☕&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;💙&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;We believe happy nurses = better care. Radical idea, right? 🤝 A supportive, team-first culture—no egos, no nonsense, we keep it real at IntelliChoice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;❤️ Proudly Celebrating 17 Years of Great Care❤️&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;At IntelliChoice Home Care, you’re more than a nurse - you’re part of our family that values compassion, transparency, and support.&amp;nbsp; We just celebrated 17 years of care, and we did so as a small, family owned company. Nothing corporate about us! We’re not just filling shifts—we’re building meaningful relationships in our communities across North Carolina.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;You’re not “just staff.” You’re the kind of human we cheer for, invest in, and brag about. We celebrate wins, support each other, and make sure you love BOTH your job &lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt; your schedule&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(186, 55, 42); text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Why Nurses Choose IntelliChoice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;✔️&lt;/strong&gt;Your Schedule, Your Way – No burnout. YOU CHOOSE your cases, shifts, and patient type (Adult or Pediatric).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;✔️One-on-One Care – No juggling six patients. No running through hallways. Just quality care in the home..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;✔️Great Pay + Benefits – Weekly pay, bonuses, and incentives for high-need cases. FREE Vitable Primary Care (telehealth, mental health coaching, prescriptions &amp;amp; labs for eligible full-time staff)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;✔️24/7 Rockstar Support – Respiratory experts + clinical team always available (and yes, you can actually call the CEO!).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;✔️Growth That Matters – Ongoing training, mentorship, clinical support, and career advancement. New to trach/vent? Been a minute? We GOT YOU and provide FULL training and support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;✔️SAFETY FIRST and ALWAYS – We do a thorough intake, and inspect EVERY home before any visit. Your safety is a priority here. You meet and accept the cases you are comfortable taking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🩺Your Role 🩺&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide individualized care to patients with complex medical needs (including trach/vent) across all ages, while supporting families and ensuring safe, high-quality care. Been a while or next worked with trach/vent but want to learn? We GOT YOU! This is a place where we support skill growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
