&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;520&quot; data-end=&quot;560&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;Why Nurses Choose IntelliChoice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
