&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;❤️ Proudly Celebrating 17 Years of Care ❤️&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Let&#39;s talk about one of the reasons so many nurses fall in love with home care...&amp;nbsp;The opportunity to truly focus on one patient at a time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for compassionate RNs and LPNs to support an adult patient who needs a dedicated nurse by his side during the overnight hours. If you enjoy building meaningful relationships, providing attentive care, and having the time to focus on your patient instead of juggling multiple assignments, this could be the perfect fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Available Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 🌙 Only 3 Nights a Week... Leaving more time for you!&amp;nbsp;🌙&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(186, 55, 42);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If overnight shifts aren&#39;t your thing, no worries - we have days, nights, full-time, part-time, and PRN opportunities available across North Carolina. Let&#39;s find the right fit for you!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
