&lt;li data-start=&quot;1117&quot; data-end=&quot;1248&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great Pay + Benefits – &lt;/strong&gt;Weekly pay, bonuses, and incentives for high-need cases. FREE Vitable Primary Care (telehealth, mental health coaching, prescriptions &amp;amp; labs for eligible full-time staff)&lt;/li&gt;
